OL,3,CSenedd to increase number of
OL,4,Cpoliticians and change voting system
OL,6,FSenedd members have voted to back
OL,7,Fplans to increase the number of Senedd
OL,8,Fmembers and to change the votes
OL,9,Fsystem. 43 members voted for it while
OL,10,F16 - the Conservatives - voted
OL,11,Fagainst. It needed 40 members to pass.
OL,12,FThe bill will now go to the King for
OL,13,FRoyal Assent which is expected in June
OL,14,For July. It then becomes law which
OL,15,Fwill pave the way for the changes to
OL,16,Fbe introduced in time for the 2026
OL,17,FSenedd election.
OL,19,FUnder the new 'closed list' voting
OL,20,Fsystem, the public will vote for
OL,21,Fparties rather than individuals.
