OL,3,CSenedd to increase number of
OL,4,Cpoliticians and change voting system
OL,6,FThe country will be split into 16
OL,7,Flarge constituencies, instead of the
OL,8,Fcurrent 40 and five regions, and each
OL,9,Fconstituency will have six elected
OL,10,Fmembers.
OL,12,FIt means that total number of
OL,13,Fpoliticians will rise from 60 to 96 at
OL,14,Fthe next Senedd election in or before
OL,15,FMay 2026.
