OL,3,CSenedd to increase number of
OL,4,Cpoliticians and change voting system
OL,6,FThe change was proposed as part of the
OL,7,FWelsh Government's co-operation
OL,8,Fagreement with Plaid Cymru, who argue
OL,9,Fas the powers of the Senedd have grown
OL,10,Fsince devolution, so has the workload
OL,11,Fon politicians.
OL,13,FThey believe in order for the Welsh
OL,14,FParliament to continue to function
OL,15,Fthere needs to be more representatives
OL,16,Fin Y Siambr (the chamber).
