OL,3,CSenedd to increase number of
OL,4,Cpoliticians and change voting system
OL,6,FCommenting on the results, Elin Jones
OL,7,FMS, Llywydd of the Senedd said: "As we
OL,8,Fmark 25 years of devolution this week,
OL,9,Ftoday's vote represents the start of
OL,10,Fthe next chapter in the story of
OL,11,FWales' democracy."
OL,13,F"The Senedd today is a very different
OL,14,Fplace compared with the National
OL,15,FAssembly of 1999. We now have a fully-
OL,16,Ffledged parliament with law-making and
OL,17,Ftax-varying powers, but our capacity
OL,18,Fto represent the people of Wales and
OL,19,Fto hold the government to account
OL,20,Fhasn't grown at the same pace."
