OL,6,FShe added: "The changes supported
OL,7,Ftoday by a clear majority of Members
OL,8,Fwill ensure a stronger, more effective
OL,9,FSenedd for the 21st century."
OL,11,FPlaid Cymru Leader Rhun ap Iorwerth MS
OL,12,Fsaid the bill paved the way for a
OL,13,Fparliament "fit for the 21st century"
OL,14,Fand provided a new foundation to build
OL,15,Fa fairer Wales and to prepare for
OL,16,Fpolitical and constitutional change.
OL,18,FHowever opponents to the changes argue
OL,19,Fthe new systems is less democratic and
OL,20,Fshould not be high up the Welsh
OL,21,FGovernment's priority list.
