OL,6,FDarren Millar MS, Welsh Conservative
OL,7,FShadow Minister for the Constitution,
OL,8,Fsaid: "The #120 million plan for more
OL,9,Fpoliticians, more fancy offices and a
OL,10,Flarger Senedd are the furthest thing
OL,11,Ffrom the Welsh people's priorities,
OL,12,Fbut that's what Labour and Plaid have
OL,13,Fpushed through today.
OL,15,F"I have said it before and I will say
OL,16,Fit again. Wales desperately needs more
OL,17,Fdoctors, dentists, nurses and
OL,18,Fteachers, not Labour and Plaid's plans
OL,19,Fto spend millions on more politicians."
