OL,6,FAndrew RT Davies MS, Leader of the
OL,7,FWelsh Conservatives, referred to the
OL,8,Fchanges as "a national embarrassment",
OL,9,Fstating: "Our Welsh NHS is on its
OL,10,Fknees, educational attainment is
OL,11,Fcollapsing and employment numbers are
OL,12,Fplummeting, but this vanity project is
OL,13,FLabour and Plaid's top priority.
OL,15,F"The Welsh Conservatives would reverse
OL,16,Fthese plans and spend the money on our
OL,17,Fhealth service instead."
